### 获取所有考试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/exams
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据ID获取考试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/exams/EXAM_001
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加考试
POST http://localhost:8080/api/exams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "examId": "EXAM_TEST",
  "classId": "CLASS_TEST",
  "classroomId": "ROOM_TEST",
  "examDate": "2023-06-15",
  "periods": 120
}

### 更新考试
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/exams/EXAM_TEST
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "COURSE_TEST",
  "examDate": "2023-06-16",
  "examType": "期末考试",
  "duration": 150
}

### 删除考试
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/exams/EXAM_TEST
Content-Type: application/json
